  sugar: 33 g
  protein: 33 g
  sodium: 750 g
time required: 40 minutes
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/cherry-ancho-duck-breats-5e285ff71589430a16182d4d
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
